        "subject": "LU-5777 quota: reserve enough credits for setattr",
        "message": "LU-5777 quota: reserve enough credits for setattr\n\nOn chown/chgrp operation, the file to be changed could be the\nlast file of owner/group, and the user/group ID entry could be\nremoved from the quota file in this setattr operation. We'd\nreserve enough journal credits for such case.\n\nLustre-commit: ac6814575513471df5e4e452ab2894787f744b99\nLustre-change: http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/12361/\n\nSigned-off-by: Niu Yawei <yawei.niu@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Ie87c27c53a576db81b30ac43ba8e3ff559fc0ec4\nReviewed-on: http://review.whamcloud.com/12473\nReviewed-by: Alex Zhuravlev <alexey.zhuravlev@intel.com>\nReviewed-by: Bobi Jam <bobijam@gmail.com>\nTested-by: Jenkins\nTested-by: Maloo <hpdd-maloo@intel.com>\nReviewed-by: Oleg Drokin <oleg.drokin@intel.com>\n"
      },
